    <section id="id1163716818715">
      <title>Materials (for a class of 25)</title>
      <para id="id1163710392729">• Computer/projection screen</para>
      <para id="id5398576">• Access to Brainpop.com</para>
      <para id="id1163712615204">• Hygrometer (1 per class)</para>
      <para id="id1163709379968">•  Infrared Thermometer (1 per class)</para>
      <para id="id5479122">•  Ozone Test Strips (1 per class)</para>
      <para id="id1163709438046">•  Ozone Scanner (1 per class)</para>
      <para id="id1163714603614">•  Wind Vane (1 per class)</para>
      <para id="id1163716853403">•  Thermal Glove (1 per class)</para>
      <para id="id1163709601554">• GLOBE Measurement Data Sheets (1 per student)</para>
    </section>
