      <section id="id1163711205129">
        <title>Expected Outcomes</title>
        <list id="id1163713569858" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
          <item>Students measure ozone and meteorology conditions for the first time.</item>
          <item>Students label the five layers of the atmosphere and know what can be found in each layer of the atmosphere. </item>
          <item>Students can draw and describe an urban heat island.</item>
          <item>Students can draw and label the components of a sea breeze circulation.</item>
          <item>Students should complete Lesson Two Journal Activities.</item>
        </list>
      </section>
